extendedInfo.description: HuntCast 2013 by DataSport is the best hunting forecast app for the Android by a long shot. DataSport has been creating hunting forecast graphs for over 38 years. Now you can have their tried and true hunting forecast on your Android Handset. Get HuntCast today and maximize your time spent in the outdoors.HuntCast 2013 shows forecasts for Dec 1st 2012 through Jan 31st 2014
